description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Staff Nurse | Paramedic | Excellent Training and Development opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overtime offered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set shift patterns of 4 on, 4 off to support work/life balance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;42 hours a week on an 8 week rolling rota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 hour paid lunch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Buddy programme to support with induction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5% pension contributions by employee and matched by Mitie&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shares, Life insurance &amp; Private Medical Cover&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Market leading HCP led model enabling career progression and continuous professional development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MiDeals discount scheme with over 3000 offers available from your favourite retailers, leisure, and utilities companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we&#39;re looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in working with challenging behaviours and vulnerable people (Essential)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Registered Nurse or Paramedic with at least 2 years post-qualification experience (Essential)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of A&amp;E, Primary Care, Substance Misuse, Walk in or Urgent Care (Desirable)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties and responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assessment &amp; care of detaineesand staff in custody suites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forensic sampling, including road traffic offence bloods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mental health and substance misuse assessments and management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Providing substance misuse therapies whilst in custody.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Healthcare promotion, brief interventions &amp; self-harm reduction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Referrals and Signposting to support wider vulnerabilities the reduction of re-offending.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a competitive salary in addition tobenefits including pension schemes, private medical cover, share schemes and MiDeals discount scheme with over 3000 offers available from your favourite retailers, leisure, and utilities companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Police Vetting Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Right to work in the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously resided in the UK for the previous 3 years, with no more than 3 months spent overseas at any one time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full UK driving license.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active PIN &amp; full membership of the HCPC (Paramedic), or NMC (RGN) with no restriction on practice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility to move across Merseyside Custody Suites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Care &amp; Custody, a Mitie company&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
